+- The recommendation order is explicit: `주도섹터 -> 실적 -> OPM -> VCS -> RS -> 자리/이격 -> 수급`.
+
+If this policy changes again, update `docs/briefing_logic_v2.md` and the selection tests first, then refresh the automation notes.
